ZH: 我们需要对计划进行变更。
EN: We need to make changes to the plan.

ZH: 最近公司发生了一些重大变更。
EN: There have been some significant changes in the company recently.

ZH: 他提议对会议的时间进行变更。
EN: He suggested a change in the time of the meeting.

ZH: 换个思路，或许能获得更好的变更。
EN: Changing the approach might lead to a better change.

ZH: 我们必须适应环境变更。
EN: We need to adapt to the changes in the environment.

ZH: 这次变更将会有深远的影响。
EN: This change will have far-reaching implications.

ZH: 政府宣布了一项法律变更。
EN: The government announced a legal change.

ZH: 尽管遭遇许多变更，他们仍然坚定不移地前进。
EN: Despite facing many changes, they continue to move forward resolutely.

