EN: Please refrain from making judgments before understanding all the changes.

ZH: 我们需要跟进市场变更来保持竞争力。
EN: We need to keep up with market changes to stay competitive.

ZH: 我们正在评估对产品进行的变更是否会对销售产生积极影响。
EN: We are evaluating whether the changes made to the product will have a positive impact on sales.

